CE.config);\\r\\n    }\\r\\n}\\r\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777723488849}}\n1479:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"**Investigating MonetaryConfig**\\n\\nI'm thinking about why the system property doesn't seem to affect MonetaryConfig anymore. I wonder if MonetaryConfig caches values at static load from the javamoney.properties file or if there's an issue with the priority of the property keys. It looks like I need to inspect MonetaryConfig more closely to understand how it processes these properties. Let's dig into this and see what I can find!\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0a83b75ce14898880169f5e85dee1c8197904817f0d8c9ee36\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp9ehgFdgV6CU0PP4EhmQnmiX1MyLByDGTDUSw6i9y1UJuc9oEQeLem2ObhQpIZHYv042MpchRfRdES8ROGK7emIRG23qJsTrK0kF8OAtX2GeC1nXGiasZvJjVsjq_G-2LqdwS_-cVvIsfIzMnBIz4kAiFOE4ty9nhi4SjPRIEoxedrKlyPx0oG5Zl83F96vqcf2lDVslIc1o2MyM2ZXv-FImApaKvTFLLOiUJaXm9X4GvxYpVlU8lJq8AWBQjVS9gjcMYxeJGvboQFyVQOi5jMi1Y57A7pZUx49xO4VDHITf83bqqjk3ToMfs0HM8Z8S_Z3BcdHrnAtsixA6zMsa9DrtKUNi9naH6oZYFX5JHxGRHess-odnxzPI9UBclpp5sheWVE-DtB_A83pPRyxmD33TdVnll1-OxoaoJSt29MFbFjfKh6nVa4gcSqmxbRFOKj3NPbcSAwQs5YiiBR6rmzr9_H8zu7ScvFx_nBU6aj-rSCCg8-2TnvIvL51LcgzzA73sS-iuAiv0wly2m86ZR1n2yUdIsNpDxANtXnNZES_Q1GRXH5Qecd5ySGZSYDvZSdzQGgdHLFzByMHWHsAoa3NoFfyAxCVk2vNohi-W3qeEMYzsEZtGL8uJxn_45FmTsA5uMYRnLKiphLlnJDr0wd6elu8wBShcT_ph1A3Po6oTMAVtF2Ce4cWgYI5BSKPCKLDokN_uMP6mEAzgYYgrY53Tk8WPYzOUhlNlJ-kPvB_vxC4fTkzkbDLdeB4TSPqa253_6zdQsLW1M-dR1kmUXR7KVIXXFza_c4vlfgs3KSnSqlmZMkByHHIj4JWhrdc7BQKPJnV7YGOqgGW-LBwM9bh3HUyFrh8wA_nWUrE4Onr4yovL6in-Ni-ElbxesA6Oqu7gY2ALf72B4mmdq4SlbFFb83Mi0xTmoT7jhGIl0g10owG7rCdDe9RMK_3Ls36FffHVQJa0SRf2AQbmIlZ06j9pNXW_FZ_ktYumYQAehlcym9V_veAr9jxK1jWA3X9Pd6rlX9RFRNSmn__ANlhpHaCnfktoU14fhKwRzcFDT0AD3riUolYxbGlB9fel3Dl0WYwayOr0bYKT5n9Zc84lVC0z4BR415WJCIq8ayW_n7uBJ39nTj4BKkszKEIvJNcVbYHFrHJbivI42HTS6o